  directory.
  Use FindData to determine the characteristics of the directory that has been found.

  Parameter AName indicates the directory. If soStripDirs is excluded from Options, AName includes
  the full directory path of the directory.
See Also
  TJvSearchFiles.OnBeginScanDir, TJvSearchFiles.OnFindFile, TJvSearchFiles.Options

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
